<a href="http://planetgreen.discovery.com/food-health/8-benefits-of-home-cooking.html">8 Benefits of Home Cooking</a><br />
<a href="http://planetgreen.discovery.com/food-health/appear-on-emeril-green.html">Have Emeril Solve Your Cooking Challenges</a></p>
            	
            </div>

